UNITED STATES of America v. Lena G. CLARKE and John Skinner, Executor of the Estate of Frank C. Clarke. No. 513. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth. Circuit. July 20, 1931. S. M. Brewster, U. S. Atty., of Topeka, Kan., for appellant. U. S. Weary, of Junction City, Kan., for appellees.

Before LEWIS and McDERMOTT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on motion of appellant.
